Notes

Mogri is positioned at 0 to reflect its role as foundational container rather than derivative primitive.

CSP-100 preserves the operational lattice of CSP-106 while removing mythic/runtime extensions.

This document defines the modeling core only.

Extensions (dragonruntime, goddess layer, cross-time layers) are external modules.
